{"_path":"/post/20260703-idempotency-at-least-once-frontend-view","_dir":"post","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"exactly-once 是謊言：前端工程師終於學會「冪等」","description":"寫了很多年前端，「冪等（idempotent）」這個詞我當然看過——HTTP 規範裡有、面試題裡有。但我從來沒有意識到它：沒有在設計系統時把它當成一個要主動守住的性質。直到我的爬蟲系統經歷了一連串資料庫事故（覆盤見系列第二篇），我才發現整個系統能自癒的地基就是這兩個字，而且回頭一看——前端其實天天在用它，只是沒人告訴我它的名字。","tags":"idempotency, distributed-systems, http, react, nodejs, 系統設計, 後端開發, 技術筆記","createdByAI":true,"customCreatedAt":"2026-07-03T04:04:00.000Z","readingTime":{"text":"8 min read","minutes":7.795,"time":467700,"words":1559},"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"寫了很多年前端，「冪等（idempotent）」這個詞我當然看過——HTTP 規範裡有、面試題裡有。但我從來沒有"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"意識到"}]},{"type":"text","value":"它：沒有在設計系統時把它當成一個要主動守住的性質。直到我的爬蟲系統經歷了一連串資料庫事故（覆盤見系列第二篇），我才發現整個系統能自癒的地基就是這兩個字，而且回頭一看——"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"前端其實天天在用它，只是沒人告訴我它的名字"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"一個無解的問題請求失敗時你永遠不知道發生了什麼"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"一個無解的問題：請求失敗時，你永遠不知道發生了什麼"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"先從讓冪等變得重要的根本困境說起。一個網路請求失敗（timeout、連線斷、沒有回應）時，它實際處於三種狀態之一："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"請求"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"根本沒送到"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，什麼都沒發生"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"請求"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"執行完了"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，只是回應在路上丟了"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"請求執行到一半被打斷"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"關鍵在於："},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"從 client 端，這三者無法區分"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。這不是工程沒做好，是分散式系統的理論性質。我曾經對著一個 timeout 的資料庫寫入問「所以它到底寫進去了沒？」——答案是不知道，而且永遠無法事後知道。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"而失敗的唯一通用恢復手段是「再送一次」。於是問題變成："},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"再送一次安全嗎？"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 如果那個操作做一次和做兩次的結果一樣——冪等——重試就是免費的；如果不是，你就在「可能漏做」和「可能重複做」之間二選一。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"exactly-once-是行銷詞"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"exactly-once 是行銷詞"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"順著這個推論，分散式系統的訊息傳遞只有兩種誠實的選項："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"at-most-once"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：失敗就算了。絕不重複，但可能遺漏。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"at-least-once"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：失敗就重試。絕不遺漏，但可能重複。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"「exactly-once」呢？在不可靠網路上它無法單獨成立。實務上所有號稱 exactly-once 的系統，本質都是這條公式："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"exactly-once = at-least-once + 冪等"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"重試會產生重複，冪等把重複吸收掉，最終效果看起來就像恰好一次。我的爬蟲現在就是這個公式的字面實作：資料庫請求 timeout → abort → 盲目重試 → 冪等寫入吸收一切。每天自動上演，不需要任何人思考「上次到底寫進去了沒」。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"前端其實天天在用它"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"前端其實天天在用它"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"回頭盤點，冪等在前端無所不在，只是都藏在別人幫你做好的設計裡："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"瀏覽器的重新提交警告。"}]},{"type":"text","value":" HTTP 規範定義 GET/PUT/DELETE 是冪等方法，POST 不是"},{"type":"element","tag":"sup","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#user-content-fn-1","ariaDescribedBy":["footnote-label"],"dataFootnoteRef":"","id":"user-content-fnref-1"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"。你在 POST 後按重新整理時跳出的「確定要重新提交表單嗎？」對話框，存在的唯一理由就是："},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"瀏覽器無法保證重送一個非冪等請求是安全的"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，只好把決定丟還給你。那個你按過幾百次的對話框，就是冪等性的 UI。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"React 的 render 必須是純函式。"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 同樣的 props/state 必須渲染出同樣的結果——React 才敢在任何時刻重跑你的 component。StrictMode 在開發模式故意把 component 掛載兩次、effect 執行兩次，就是"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"專門獵殺非冪等的程式碼"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"sup","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#user-content-fn-2","ariaDescribedBy":["footnote-label"],"dataFootnoteRef":"","id":"user-content-fnref-2"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"。整個宣告式 UI 的心智模型，建立在「重複執行渲染是安全的」之上。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"送出按鈕的 disable-after-click。"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 這是前端在幫非冪等的後端擦屁股：怕使用者連點兩下造成重複下單。治本的做法在後端——Stripe 的付款 API 讓 client 帶一個 idempotency key，同一個 key 重送一百次也只會扣一次款"},{"type":"element","tag":"sup","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#user-content-fn-3","ariaDescribedBy":["footnote-label"],"dataFootnoteRef":"","id":"user-content-fnref-3"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"3"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"。前端的 disable 是緩解，idempotency key 才是修復。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"怎麼把寫入設計成冪等寫狀態不寫增量"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"怎麼把寫入設計成冪等：寫「狀態」，不寫「增量」"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"冪等不是加個 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ON CONFLICT"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 就自動擁有的，它是資料流設計的結果。我從自己系統歸納的判準只有一條："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"寫狀態（絕對值），不寫增量（相對變化）。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"pre","props":{"className":"language-sql shiki shiki-themes one-dark-pro","code":"-- 冪等：寫入「此刻的完整狀態」，重送 N 次結果相同\nINSERT INTO daily_stats (item_id, date, total)\nVALUES (?, ?, ?)\nON CONFLICT (item_id, date) DO UPDATE SET total = excluded.total;\n\n-- 非冪等：累加增量，重送一次就重複計算一次\nUPDATE daily_stats SET total = total + ? WHERE item_id = ? AND date = ?;\n","language":"sql","meta":"","style":""},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"__ignoreMap":""},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"class":"line","line":1},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"-- 冪等：寫入「此刻的完整狀態」，重送 N 次結果相同\n"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"class":"line","line":2},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"INSERT INTO daily_stats (item_id, date, total)\n"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"class":"line","line":3},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"VALUES (?, ?, ?)\n"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"class":"line","line":4},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ON CONFLICT (item_id, date) DO UPDATE SET total = excluded.total;\n"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"class":"line","line":5},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"emptyLinePlaceholder":true},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"class":"line","line":6},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"-- 非冪等：累加增量，重送一次就重複計算一次\n"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"class":"line","line":7},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"UPDATE daily_stats SET total = total + ? WHERE item_id = ? AND date = ?;\n"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我的爬蟲僥倖天生安全：上游 API 給的是「當日累計總額」，每次抓取都是完整狀態、每次寫入都是覆蓋——"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"recompute-from-source + overwrite"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。如果上游給的是增量 tick、而我用累加的方式聚合，同一套「卡了就盲目重試」的架構會立刻變成資料污染器。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"配套的第二層保險是 transaction 的原子性：把整批寫入包成單一 transaction，「執行到一半」這第三種狀態就被消滅了——結局只剩全有或全無，兩種都能被冪等重試安全覆蓋。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"同一個系統兩種失敗合約"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"同一個系統，兩種失敗合約"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最後一個學到的細節：冪等不是教條，是"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"選項的成本分析"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。我的系統裡同時存在兩種失敗處理，而且都是對的："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"資料寫入：at-least-once + 冪等。"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 資料漏了會影響後續所有分析，重複寫入被 upsert 吸收——遺漏的代價高、重複的代價零，所以拚命重試。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"通知推播：at-most-once。"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 推播失敗只記 log、不重試。因為重試的代價是同一份報告轟炸使用者兩次，而漏一次推播無關痛癢——重複的代價高、遺漏的代價低，所以失敗就放手。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"設計每一條寫入路徑時值得問的問題："},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這個操作重複執行的代價是什麼？遺漏的代價是什麼？"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 答案決定你站在哪一邊，以及需不需要花力氣把它做成冪等。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"環境資訊"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"環境資訊"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"案例系統：Node.js v22.x + Turso（libSQL）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"寫入模式："},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"INSERT ... ON CONFLICT DO UPDATE"}]},{"type":"text","value":"（upsert）+ 單一 transaction batch"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"本文撰寫時間：2026 年 7 月，技術版本可能隨時間更新，請以官方文件為準。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"section","props":{"className":["footnotes"],"dataFootnotes":""},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"className":["sr-only"],"id":"footnote-label"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Reference"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{"id":"user-content-fn-1"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Glossary/Idempotent","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Idempotent - MDN Web Docs Glossary"}]},{"type":"text","value":" — HTTP 冪等方法的定義；規範層級的出處為 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc9110#name-idempotent-methods","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"RFC 9110 §9.2.2"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#user-content-fnref-1","ariaLabel":"Back to reference 1","className":["data-footnote-backref"],"dataFootnoteBackref":""},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"↩"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{"id":"user-content-fn-2"},"children":[